4","tid":2071340,"uid":329335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59121402d25a0ad7871ce94468b6a6611e2bed1f","tid":2071340,"uid":135359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:31:53.000Z","msg":"我都係 身邊周學今年grad<br />\n但我仲要defer...<br />\n遲一年畢業就少一年經驗 又冇長處<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:07:04.000Z","msg":"都唔知點同人爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3edacd75a34bb5b38a4c1740e76f76c19bd1c6","tid":2071340,"uid":244876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:20:24.000Z","msg":"曾經叫做只呵唔鬧既樹窿重生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次為左比真係有需要既人真係有個窿去放負，求開解<br />\n重生之餘會整多左少少要求比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能會覺得咁樣做好麻煩，但係admin們都睇到係任意比大家入既結果就係會有好多人唔係真係想去幫人<br />\n而係去做好多野騷擾人，而始終人手有限好難逐一調停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次會有張非常簡單既表格比大家填  我地好希望人來既係有需要被大家幫手又或者去幫下身邊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近期發生太多好負面既野，社會既情況好令人感到無力，失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬥黃情況甚多，灰心絕望都不在少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知以前個樹窿grp幫到幾多人  不過我個人就本住大家都係手足，大家都有需要幫忙既時刻<br />\n好似熊仔頭其中一條片咁  幫到人唔係令到自己開心 係想人地都開心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlink就係到: 有需要就填一填交比admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/ko4G3auwF5yyYPvk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fko4G3auwF5yyYPvk7&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2wzH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e4ad6def\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/ko4G3auwF5yyYPvk7</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係到都唔想講咩太沉重既野<br />\n只係希望大家仲記得過去發生既野，大家既付出同努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf8b675e44cc9b8e3f3ddae11e61ef6c1051dd6","tid":2071340,"uid":193135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b2aa2119112cf89295acd537cfd508ca1d90925","tid":2071340,"uid":6473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"da7b700d01e5c55b42d33f5fc2b87da6af82da4a","tid":2071340,"uid":329335,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7c73ee1d8266a237f2a691da6dbf03fd00cb591","tid":2071340,"uid":242117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:41:58.000Z","msg":"讀緊書？做緊野？<br />\n有細藝或者興趣搞下日子會好過d"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T18:57:30.000Z","msg":"見到身邊啲fd搵到intern或者鋪好左grad之後條路就覺得自己好廢 仲係到做緊廢青"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T19:04:20.000Z","msg":"28歲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T20:30:21.000Z","msg":"你有冇睇心理醫生，我正諗緊睇唔睇好，成日覺得好呃錢，800/55 mins<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97169d02a4cc0702b810a366cd5453d3b80579e","tid":2071340,"uid":1